data.description: This beautiful home was built in 2017,It  features 4 bedrooms, and 2 full baths. Slipt bedrooms with open concept living area,  Moderiate cosmetic upgrades help make this property move in ready. Conveniently located to: Great restaurants, Retail Shopping, and just a short drive to the beach, This move in ready property is your blank canvas to create your forever home.
